Cam::

She finally went to the med bay and saw Blackfang standing there. She 
was panting hard and her lead was dropping from running all over the 
base. "I couln't find Kenzo.*pant pant*  So I wanted to come back and 
*pant pant* help out here."  She heard noices coming from the CR 
chamber and looked up at Blackfang. "So, can we keep her? If we do, 
then it would be three canine bots here. Wouldn't it be fun? we could 
run together, play together, be a pack together. What'da say 
Blackfang? You can play daddy, I can be the baby and she can be the 
mommy."  Her little fox kit face was bright with delight. She started 
jumping and hopping around the room with a new found energy.
